The paper evaluates database management systems (DBMSs) and libraries for large-scale image analysis, which suggests a focus on data management and computer vision. Therefore, cs.DB and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses performance and efficiency, which could fall under cs.DC and cs.LG.
